Pinuntahan ko si mama.

617
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:36,320
Mukha siyang haggard.

618
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:41,480
Siguro...

619
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,720
meron siyang...

620
00:37:45,440 --> 00:37:46,560
